  "body": "We want to promote inside status app, the possibility to upgrade the account security by using a keycard. This includes:\n\n* explain to the user benefits \n* call to action to get a keycard\n\nThis encounters three things:\n**i/** a banner inside the app that promotes to the user to increase his security with a keycard \n**ii/** a landing page explaining with more details what his keycard and how it helps the user with his security and calls to action to purchase one \n**iii/** user is then on a shopping site and we must be able to track conversions \n\n**For an MVP we want to do the following:**\n**i/** have a banner _on the login screen_. Proposed design here: \nbanners : \n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11461437/100632265-ecd6a680-332c-11eb-8864-df1ce84ee1b2.png)\n\nin the logins screen here: \n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11461437/100632213-dd575d80-332c-11eb-9035-971a183ae124.png)\n\n**ii/** landing page can be a duplicate of https://status.im/keycard-integration\n**iii/** shopify site remains as is, and tracking of conversions is done from shopify \n\n**To do**\n\n* [x] [X ] create the landing page (guylouis + aleks) and provide URL\nupdate (09/12): the URL is https://get-keycard.status.im/\n* [x]  implement the banner in the app\n\n",
